Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在嫦娥镇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然住宅区域发展得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在稍微远一点的地方  大自然还保留得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气那么好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是因为我平日行善的缘故哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿忘记做作业让要同学借你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿第二节课休息就把便当吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.38,0:01:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小博好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁过分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许的确如博士君所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  小要到底是哪一边的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个香味  是八朔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.03,0:01:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:32.87,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:36.99,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.51,0:03:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了哦  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好难受的  小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃真精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真没精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小铃的兴致太高了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服吧  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  集合~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己来准备材料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼当然要新鲜的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好大一条
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大收获
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  小要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钓到了  钓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  博士君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鱼都不去博士君那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.98,0:05:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了会分给他的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的  好像较上劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别钓了  回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有见到那么高兴的麻奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  这里真是个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说过的嫦娥狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前似乎也是生活在这一带的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们所居住的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被包围在森林和自然中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得好像是被关起来了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这名为自然的巨大笼子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那个…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸当真的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是因为要同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是诗歌  诗歌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…听起来不像是诗歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小铃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到刚才还在这里组装烤肉架来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微去找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么只有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现变态  发现变态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始击退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个装扮怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌呀  小博不要这样盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  为什么是泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来烤肉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君  找到小铃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要同学你来说说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃居然穿泳装…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管那么多  过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没带泳装来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣裤好不容易才干的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得那么好的天气  马上就会干的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博生气了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  不用这样道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  做了错事就要好好道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小博  就以此原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗  原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信小铃的话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的以为我会让你看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要戏弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  八朔是拿来当点心？还是要烤？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤？怎么可能做那种遭天谴的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭天谴…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在八朔上画脸就不会遭天谴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我专用的特别标志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  快盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.99,0:10:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好饱  好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都吃完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿去称下体重  脸就会发青了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真是美味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢烧烤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.98,0:10:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.61,0:10:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我洗过后再送还
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  就这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样博士君的气味就会留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又说奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的  开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.61,0:10:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥的玩笑有时很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上小博的衣服和我决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃也够奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自拿我赌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累坏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.81,0:11:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这样道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和博士君在一起我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.45,0:11:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  小铃钓到了那么大的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而哥哥却一条都没钓到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是手感不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  连鱼饵的蚯蚓都不敢拿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要让小铃来替你上饵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧  小博
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕流个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子也有点晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是发烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还算勉强撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来非得好好道个歉不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小博  作为赔礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.87,0:12:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可真无力吐槽了  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病得不轻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去「中心」一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「中心」？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「嫦娥医疗中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一家综合性医院  我们都叫它「中心」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面最新设备一应俱全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是家挺有规模的医院
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  还是去看看医生比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就跟你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人也能去的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是小铃你在医院里被传染了感冒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.46,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不好办了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃  你保护过头了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的跟要同学说的一样  好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  来这儿的人也真不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:13:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有劳您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:14:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是九澄博士对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的事情  我已经从侄女那儿听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侄女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,栉名田…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眠她是我的侄女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.74,0:14:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听眠说  班上新转来了个奇怪的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「奇怪的同学」…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在本人面前说他是「奇怪的同学」  的确有些失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒啊  要不要先验个血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,验血？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.62,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给你开了些药  回去的时候去药店取吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  就开始抽血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是方便的话  一起如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是院长栉名田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下贤木
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你们生物制药公司的负责人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是境井先生才对啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  不过从今以后  就都由在下来接洽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这交接可真突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一些公司内部的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没的事  没的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下手上的这份  姑且就算是敝社的产品介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑且」这话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好像有点缺乏职业作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的  敝社预定今后要加大新药的研发力度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  这或许能够对院长您的研究有所助益
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定不负厚望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.64,0:15:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她给你添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈也感冒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我是来取一些常用的药的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常用的药？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.59,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…  是不是哪里有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心我的身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你可真会体贴人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  博士君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小铃她  已经吻过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「难不成」  是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如说  难不成  你对女孩子不感兴趣之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你看啊  虽说是我这个做哥的一面之词吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她也确实挺漂亮的对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.35,0:16:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可尽管如此  尽管她对你是那样的穷追不舍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对她却仍旧是坐怀不乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:16:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺奇怪的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这路没走错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么要紧事赶着回去办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是稍微兜了下风而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  我是想能够像这样  与你单独相处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君你的香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  哎…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…  住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不要…  啊…  啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不行…  你…  住手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.94,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.28,0:18:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.47,0:18:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  啊…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃她也有说过  你很容易上当呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:18:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  那孩子来了医院一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那孩子」是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九澄博士么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.99,0:19:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  跟小眠你说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏又是在这个八朔收成不好的年景里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了个那样的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道小眠你也不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.97,0:19:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还是拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是让一诚大哥送你回来的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥你也太偷奸耍滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是也发了烧  去了医院就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真能说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都说什么「去了反而身体会更不好」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  有这事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  朝三暮四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早点睡可对身体不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我弄醒的好像就是你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.19,0:21:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已经好了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.41,0:21:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别大意了  还是吃点药比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.95,0:21:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧好像退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  似乎还有那么点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一诚大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  我走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:18.24,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}忘れないで　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:18.24,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}勿忘怀  此相思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:28.94,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕らが信じた愛の歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:28.94,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}吾等深信之情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.19,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}抱きしめた夜には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:35.19,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}拥夜入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:38.05,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影が月でなく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:38.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}影非月  月非影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.43,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}繰り返す罪には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.43,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}罪劫轮回
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:49.99,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}戸惑いの月が満ちる　融ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.47,0:22:49.99,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}盈惑月  消无痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:56.83,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いくつものこころが　君を縛るなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.94,0:22:56.83,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}千千心结若缚君
